metadata.name: DAKARPEPE
metadata.description:
1/1 - DAKARPEPE

But....

This is not just a 1/1 DAKARPEPE, there is more to it.

Next March 31st I will compete in a race of more than 3000km through old Paris Dakar tracks and against more than 200 teams through the Morocco Desert.

What does DAKARPEPE gives you?

‚ú∂If you win of the auction, you will not only get this 1/1 DAKARPEPE but you will have a space in the car to sponsor whatever you want: your brand, your collection or directly your PFP, whatever. You will also receive images and information about the race during the competition.

All the bidders in the auction will have a small honorary sponsor but only the winner will have the big sponsorship.

More info on my twitter @chipiron_eth

I hope you enjoy DAKARPEPE as much as I have enjoyed creating it. üê∏üèÅ
